reviewText: In this out-of-print 1985 thriller: Four beautiful girls out for a weekend of camping in the desert could never dream that a chance meeting with Peter and Eric at a gas station would turn into a circus of terror. A refreshing session of skinny dipping is cut short  when the girls sense they are being watched. Shortly after, Peter and Eric capture the girls and terrorize them in a most grizzly and perverse way. A horrifying fight for survival ensues, with four desperate women against two brutal perverts............must see.
